Portfolio

Miletus - Crypto Arbitrage Trading Software Custom software using React & Javascript. Draggable & Resizeable components. Customizeable personal dashboard. My crown jewel project :) Innoblue Website - 2019 Custom website using HTML, CSS, Javascript, Git & Github.
Ease-of-use is the most important heuristic in my UI/UX design process.
Disaster Relief & Recovery Software - 2019 Hackathon project using Java, Swift, GCP & GCV. Park Ranger Manager - 2018 1st place winner in Hackathon (HackPSU). iOS application using Swift, Adobe XD & Xcode. AntEater, Shanghai Hackathon - 2019 Web application that scanned business websites using AI to find the best B2B customer for business. I created it with 2 other teammates using Python & Javascript. It was at a Hackathon I found and joined a random team at in China while studying abroad. I designed the front-end and presented the project. This Website!
